strings:
<voice_0x01001CCB><se_high>Princess Medea: Oh! I'm human again!
And I can see your face, <hero>!

<voice_0x01001CCC><se_high>Princess Medea: Is this a dream? It must be...
Can you hear my voice, <hero>?

<voice_0x01001CCD><se_high>Princess Medea: I have to admit to being a little glum.
I thought the curse would be lifted after you defeated Dhoulmagus.
<voice_0x01001CCE><se_high>Princess Medea: And now Jessica's gone, too...
<voice_0x01001CCF><se_high>Princess Medea: I wonder where she could be?

<voice_0x01001CD0><se_high>Princess Medea: Do you think this has anything to do with
the curse?
<voice_0x01001CD1><se_high>Princess Medea: I'll be praying for her safe return.
